[[File:Spiritual warrior icon.png|left]]
The '''Spiritual warrior''' is a powerful [[Slayer monsters|Slayer monster]] found in the [[God Wars Dungeon]]. There are five types of spiritual warriors: [[Saradomin]]ists, [[Zamorak]]ians, [[Bandos]]ians, [[Armadyl]]eans and [[Zaros]]ians. Spiritual warriors require 68 [[Slayer]] to kill (note Spiritual creatures cannot be given as a [[Slayer task]] if the player has not completed the [[Death Plateau]] quest). Just like [[Spiritual ranger]]s and [[Spiritual mage]]s, there are Spiritual warriors from each god.

Spiritual warriors frequently drop [[mithril equipment]], [[adamant equipment]] and [[rune equipment]], so it is advisable to bring runes for [[High Level Alchemy]].

For players killing Spiritual warriors as part of a [[Slayer task]] wanting to avoid being attacked by them, the main area contains Saradominist warriors who are often engaged in combat with other monsters.

